&none             &kp NUMBER_6  &kp NUMBER_7  &kp NUMBER_8  &kp SPACE  &kp LEFT_ALT    &none  &space_underscore  &SYM_minus  &kp RIGHT_ALT  &kp RIGHT_CONTROL  &kp LEFT_ARROW
